g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e998d614837bf4497914bca6355d903a5ff87c82","tid":1606641,"uid":128870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:21:40.000Z","msg":"一齊贏！！"},{"pid":"25e20be305bedd8dccc1f7a6970dca00f37ba8c0","tid":1606641,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabce8c7bc6e2195b9a15ca501cd0e0348f8e976","tid":1606641,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"無船搭咩 ？ 無海外巴打咩"},{"pid":"50d4fdb77b463379a3caf203bb7eab53c94c4cc3","tid":1606641,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e97dad079cbf1559b5f3c40f8af8e1d04e71bc","tid":1606641,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d86ca9fa2cc8c33637e8b1854a820b23d96e2d9","tid":1606641,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:04:56.000Z","msg":"巴打 我明你感受<br />\n我tbi 未知有冇後遺症(點解出事唔講)<br />\n同埋聽日冇得發夢但又想多啲人去個感受好差（頭再中多下重擊好易bye）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔好企咁前，長期戰黎，以後需要你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:26:07.000Z","msg":"嗱，我tbi係因為做運動出事嫁！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁打前鋒都冇得唔企得前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時睇下休戰定打住後衛先<br />\n<br />\n因為都傷得幾重(腦癇+腦積血+腦積水+臚壓過高)<br />\n醫院開sick leave都開左幾個月俾我<br />\n同重要返去再照腦同複診<br />\n有可能再加sick leave<br />\n<br />\n我都怕嚇親各位前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但總之 唔知會發生咩事 <br />\n各位要有定最壞心理打算<br />\n另外如果有傷 你有可能係踢波/打波競技程度較高嘅運動而發生意外<br />\n情況許可著住運動服飾入a&amp;e會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警崗望我一眼冇理過我<br />\n(波友講，當時已昏迷)"},{"pid":"dca8e70eb5d16abe4b32015789db800eb51bb6dd","tid":1606641,"uid":275547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20243468c8132d38745e09599809c39af12f89b7","tid":1606641,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:34:49.000Z","msg":"真係嫁各位<br />\n如果大吉利是出事<br />\n要話俾醫務人員同警察叔叔聽你係因咩非合法原因入黎，常見嘅係運動創傷<br />\n請諗定最壞後果，點present得好啲話俾人聽你係因為咩事而入黎<br />\n唔好諱疾忌醫<br />\n例如我咁 冇去醫院應該bye bye了<br />\n我入廠時已昏迷同直skip分流站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}